title: Ep. - 185 - DANCING WITH THE STARS PREMIERE REVIEW BACHELOR IN PARADISE REVIEW
description:
Slip into those dancing shoes and shine up the Mirrorball trophy, because ABC’s Dancing With the Stars is back for its 28th season. Comedian Chris Franjola reviews the show’s season premiere including Christie Brinkley’s injury, Lamar Odom’s inability to fox trot, and Ray Lewis becoming an American darling. 


Amanda Hirsch from the Not Skinny But Not Fat podcast discusses Bachelor in Paradise. 


Reality Life with Kate Casey
